divs: Sighting DetailsThese lights just appeared out of thin air while I was outside with my dogs. My dogs barked at the UFO then they started to howl and ran off whimpering. The lights hovered around then moved in patterns, I watched for what seemed to be 5 minutes in till the lights shot off and dispersal, only after they left did my two dogs stop whimpering.
Summary: I was outside when these lights showed up.
